Ruby/GnomeVFS
=============


Ruby/GnomeVFS is a Ruby binding of GnomeVFS-2.0.x.

Requirements
------------

	Ruby:		http://www.ruby-lang.org/
	GnomeVFS:	http://developer.gnome.org/doc/API/gnome-vfs/

Install
-------

	0. install ruby and GnomeVFS.
	1. ruby extconf.rb
	2. make
	3. su
	4. make install

